{"tid":828242,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"「理性討論」有無人睇完驚奇隊長預告同我反應一樣","createTime":"2018-09-19T13:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T01:30:53.000Z","uid":191403,"like":15,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c30dd2c25e30dfe4edb82478e64a9151786c1cab","tid":828242,"uid":191403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T13:48:50.000Z","msg":"我唔討論選角啦 選角呢樣好主觀 <br />\n但係成個預告我睇完既反應就係 開頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  結尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  成條完左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成條睇完我心諗:「啊，我究竟睇左乜尻？」<br />\n除左打關愛座啊婆有D反應之外 基本上我成條片都無咩情感起伏<br />\n最尾兩眼發光個到 對唔住 我真係忍唔到笑 真係太柒 <br />\n先唔評論套戲好唔好睇 但我覺得呢條預告真係設計得好差 <br />\n驚奇隊長黎講一定得兩個賣點  佢既實力有幾誇張 同 佢同個宇宙又有咩關係<br />\n實力方面就得d死人無迫力既光線射出黎 超人死光都勁過佢<br />\n作為無睇過漫畫 最好奇係羅男 係POSTER 同劇照都有出 係TRAILER無 <br />\n算啦 我最後都會乖乖地比錢入戲院<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知大家又點睇"},{"pid":"661b4bdf6e98e74f1d451f3df9967eff734be144","tid":828242,"uid":143582,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T13:59:13.000Z","msg":"似係未做好後製，用好少片剪出嚟，係咁上下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb5c379d8fc00bcc46d1f4793fd21ad53d81511","tid":828242,"uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:02:47.000Z","msg":"Marvel話ok 就ok<br />\n唔好問唔好駁"},{"pid":"1cd3424da3c48f688dcb2986f3692067a389ad5f","tid":828242,"uid":60500,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:53:57.000Z","msg":"Marvel出品狗屎都大把人爭住食所以都廢時整到咁靚<br />\n利申 食"},{"pid":"29395f9174eefbe56d4b75097c2d1e2f9a3384a3","tid":828242,"uid":54524,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T15:12:38.000Z","msg":"睇預告當睇哂套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要第一條預告"},{"pid":"90c9378a817925d63b2ee927284c1f15a9454bc7","tid":828242,"uid":60527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi